DESCRIPTION:Join us this September for a one-o
 f-a-kind fundraising event celebra
 ting the incredible diversity of o
 ur community!\n\nRepresentatives fro
 m a variety of community groups\, i
 ncluding drag\, leather/kink\, pagea
 ntry\, and more\, will come together
  for an evening of entertainment\, 
 creativity\, and charitable giving.
  Each team will support a charity 
 of their choice while showcasing t
 heir talents through performances\,
  comedy\, art\, storytelling\, and ot
 her unique acts.\n\nThis isn't just 
 a competition\, it's an opportunity
  to build connections\, break down 
 barriers\, and demonstrate what our
  community can accomplish when we 
 work together. Throughout the even
 ing\, teams will raise funds for th
 eir chosen causes\, with donations 
 helping determine the final standi
 ngs and the distribution of the fu
 ndraising pot.\n\nExpect:\n- Live per
 formances and entertainment\n- Comm
 unity leaders and personalities\n- 
 Fundraising for worthy causes\n- Su
 rprises throughout the evening\n- A
  celebration of collaboration\, cre
 ativity\, and unity\n\nWhether you're
  coming to cheer on your favorite 
 performers\, support a great cause\,
  or simply enjoy a night of incred
 ible talent\, we invite you to be p
 art of something special.\n\nTogethe
 r\, we're stronger. Together\, we ma
 ke a difference.\n\nhttps://www.face
 book.com/events/2497900580681616/
